{"type": "article", "id": 15935, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-10-12T07:46:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 17041, "name": "merry me"}, {"id": 17042, "name": "Bureau de Change"}, {"id": 17043, "name": "Efasma"}, {"id": 17044, "name": "The Darwin Sect"}, {"id": 17045, "name": "KaCaMa Design Lab"}, {"id": 14370, "name": "reebok"}, {"id": 17046, "name": "LimitEDitions"}, {"id": 17047, "name": "Michael Anastassiades"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071224409BPycvCs5mdVrQjo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\t“stool zero” by KaCaMa Design Lab\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t来自香港的设计团队 KaCaMa Design Lab 擅长利用废料加工制作产品，这套名为“stool zero”的高脚凳就是将废弃电线外的塑料壳，缝纫编织在风扇罩上的。凳子的木腿也是废旧的运货箱子上面的板条，有清爽简单的感受。而不同颜色的电线壳经过细致的搭配，能呈现出藤编的手工感，是令人亲近的设计。<a href=\"http://www.kacama.hk/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是他们的主页</a>，还有许多废物利用创造新价值的作品。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153844H5A9yLlcvsbFqr3e.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.06968215\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153845OpE0rJCZKmbLDVjl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.54889976\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061538459akpTubACG7B1RUe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153845cpQGMa3o1Crb5Vkj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153846bfFZ9zInBpdmOt8V.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tEfasma series by Bureau de Change\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是英国设计事务所 Bureau de Change 为家具品牌 Efasma 设计的一组家具，包括屏风、沙发和桌椅。特殊之处在于椅子只在两边有扶杆，下面的椅子腿以对角为支撑，所以看似坐在了一个角上。当与桌子组合时，桌子边上留出的开口能将椅子的位置固定下来，拼成了新的形状。八边形的咖啡桌变成的正方形，而长方形的餐桌就像交错叠上了两个方形，有全新的搭配。<a href=\"http://www.efasma.co.uk/product.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153846MeRVluszc5Wrmfyg.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153847Tc2wfOqh6egjiGzt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.77368421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061538473sUTqtJEkz2Rbgp7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.305\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153847YQbuMIrWzKZ8B5wV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.27666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153848aXb45B9MArmcKf6x.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153848xaLNA9cboYSZrTOq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t线条灯  by Michael Anastassiades \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t热爱玩弄线条的英国设计师 Michael Anastassiades 带来了他的新作，用黄铜杆和条状 LED 灯组成不同造型。灯有 0.5 米和 1 米两种长度，与黄铜杆的直径相同，它们时而并排时而错位，在对称与不对称当中组成有趣的平衡。细微的变化中蕴含了很大的不同，而简单的造型和孤单的投影都诠释极简的审美。<a href=\"http://studiomichaelanastassiades.com/news\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里是他的主页。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153849umxn5v4Ea1IqdlNi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.21474359\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153849h0frUKv7aQIMTNpm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.18803419\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153850HGNLypT9v6VCi0wt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153850SA8HQDv4wZ2unlg1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153851mHpr6OJQqZk1a9ij.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tThe Darwin Tank by The Darwin Sect\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t在家中拥有一个小的水族馆不是不可能，来自比利时的团队专门研究了适合水母生活的水缸，他们使用了一个泵来过滤水而不会伤害到水母，并配有 LED 灯。外面罩着的玻璃将水母放大了一倍，当灯光透过水缸照射在墙上时，映射出半透明的水母在轻盈舒展的唯美画面。直接透过水缸看事物时，也都像染上了梦幻色彩。<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/815660157/the-darwin-tank-an-original-jellyfish-tank\" target=\"_blank\">该产品正在 Kickstarter 上集资以获得进一步改善</a>。<a href=\"http://www.darwinsect.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看团队的其他作品。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061538514Hji0uOwFDdoeNxc.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153852JiN6srXtwPeC9zV3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153852QY6hlc8PvmOeLGkI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56470588\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061538533aoFp87TkZnuRl6S.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153854eiU42oxGk6DAH5cu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t动物戒指 by merry me \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一组以动物为主题的戒指，来自泰国 merry me。每一组戒指都有三个，同时佩戴在手上才能看出其中的故事。比如松鼠系列是戴在三只邻近的手指上，能看到正在偷吃松果的松鼠；而斑马、梅花鹿等系列则是在一只手指上戴三只戒指，可以调整角度组成不同的故事。戒指外层是火烤的珐琅彩，使戒指有一个亮丽的色彩。另外，每个戒指都有小的开口以适应尺码误差。<a href=\"http://pleasemerryme.taobao.com/category-654314965.htm?spm=a1z10.3-c.0.0.e2iN9L&amp;search=y&amp;catName=r+i+n+g+s++%BD%E4+%D6%B8\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153854tLrcbKsjQHqZ8NPW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69902913\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153854gol7A3BMS1Y9hpqN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62274619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153855mBJc3KO7elijVL5R.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69486824\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153856e4fadkYClUpwn0xT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83633842\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153856TXOeIibpMadm8Ec6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45769764\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061538571WGCZcoeH84Du73X.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64493759\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153857suLrpNChDyEtv0Kd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153858weiRb4xGUakNvQug.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tSulphur by LimitEDitions &amp; Reebok Classic\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t为了纪念 Reebok（锐步）的经典款型 Ventilator 25 周年，Reebok 邀请了多家品牌联合设计纪念版。这款“Sulphur”则邀请了西班牙的球鞋名店 LimitEDitions ，鞋身用绿色搭配棕色，与硫磺矿石的色调相似，整体有一种户外登山的风格，结实耐用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061538586q2nymUh4wLE1Y7M.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153859kUSFVcy7RAMxegrB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153859UomwI9pDfgs7C2Ml.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153900gLtqc6rdXuChHfnP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153900CYvWgi71kfQa8opA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}